	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utrasque tuas et penultima aprilis et 4. maii datas accepi, et nihil est, quod ad illas respondeam, nisi quod d. <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculi</persName> uxor paulatim revalescit iterum, domino sit laus, quamvis satis adhuc sit debilis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Resalutat te cum suis omnibus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae vis, ut scribam <persName type="auto_name">Michaeli Schlattero</persName>, curabo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Caeterum interea</foreign> hatt der küng uß Franckrych gester minen herren zuͦ gschriben under anderem, das der bapst selbst an keiser beger uffschlag deß concilij biß uff den ersten tag septembris, demnach das er Parma dem römschen stuͦl wider inhendig mache.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Das welle der keiser nitt thuͦn, und achte er deßhalb, das uß dem concilio gar nützit werde.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Darbi schript er auch, das <placeName type="auto_name">Meidenburg</placeName> noch starck halte und innert wenig tagen <persName type="auto_name">hertzog Moritzen</persName> vil volkh erschlagen und 6 stuck büchßen eroberet habind.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="manual">Hütt kumpt mir schriben von <persName type="auto_name">Erbio von Richenwyl</persName>, <foreign xml:lang="la">qui inter alia haec:</foreign></s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="manual">"Studiosi ex <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Wittenberga</placeName> discedentes ad nos veniunt referentes <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philippum Melanchtonem</persName> et <persName ref="p4443" cert="high">Pomeranum</persName> gymnasium reliquisse et nunc agere cum duobus capti ducis filiis in <placeName type="auto_name">Weinmar</placeName>, propterea quod <persName type="auto_name">Mauritius Wittenbergae</persName> papisticas restituerit ceremonias.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Magdeburgenses</placeName> obsessi non morantur adversariorum minas.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Caesar</persName>, cadaver vivum, solus cum mitratis illis est <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandus</persName> cum Philippo Hispanico certat de regno; ille ait se creatum in Caesarem a proceribus Germanię, is vero se natum Cęsarem; certum est."</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec <persName ref="p1010" cert="high">Erbius</persName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil praeterea nunc habeo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus, oremus, oremus extendentes puras per poenitentiam manus ad dominum, si forte misereatur nostri et parcat.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem ex me dominis et fratribus omnibus atque uxori et universae familiae dicas.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> die ascensionis dominicę 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Io[annes] Hallerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Velim te ad d. <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName> quaestorem scribere eique gratias agere pro liberalitate <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculo</persName> praestita.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fidelissimo Christi domini et ecclesiae ministro domino Heinrycho Bullingero, pastori ecclesiae Tigurinae, domino et compatri suo venerando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich an m. Heinrych Bullinger.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
